141
00:12:37,330 --> 00:12:38,940
The perpetrator remains at large!

142
00:12:39,180 --> 00:12:40,690
Extra! Extra!

143
00:12:58,480 --> 00:12:59,780
[Jiangcheng Hospital]

144
00:13:11,130 --> 00:13:11,800
Captain Wu,

145
00:13:12,570 --> 00:13:14,420
what brings you to our hospital today?

146
00:13:15,060 --> 00:13:15,810
Are you not feeling well?

147
00:13:16,780 --> 00:13:17,450
Yu Yanchuan.

148
00:13:18,380 --> 00:13:20,550
Last night, Zhong Cheng and his wife in the northern part of the city

149
00:13:20,570 --> 00:13:21,900
were murdered at home.

150
00:13:22,210 --> 00:13:24,560
Your medical kit was found at the crime scene.

151
00:13:24,930 --> 00:13:27,340
You are now a key suspect in the murder case.

152
00:13:28,330 --> 00:13:29,250
Please come with us.

153
00:13:29,990 --> 00:13:30,700
Yu Yanchuan,

154
00:13:30,970 --> 00:13:31,380
male,

155
00:13:31,610 --> 00:13:33,210
a surgeon at Jiangcheng Hospital.

156
00:13:33,570 --> 00:13:34,690
His father, Yu Zhenhai,

157
00:13:34,690 --> 00:13:37,020
is the chairman of the largest local business association.

158
00:13:37,410 --> 00:13:39,510
He's suspected of murdering the freight company owner,

159
00:13:39,570 --> 00:13:40,540
Mr. Zhong Cheng, and his wife.

160
00:13:40,710 --> 00:13:42,340
Hereby, we officially summon you.

161
00:13:44,720 --> 00:13:46,200
Miss, this way, please.

162
00:13:54,960 --> 00:13:55,900
Why is it her?

163
00:13:59,990 --> 00:14:02,440
Miss Lin, the person in front of you, is the suspect.

164
00:14:03,320 --> 00:14:04,390
Please identify him.

165
00:14:04,900 --> 00:14:05,420
Okay.
